01/12/2009
ATHENS, Greece -- A group of men set a series of nearly simultaneous fires in different parts of Thessaloniki on Monday (November 30th), causing minor damage.
One was in an office of the Daily Newspaper Publishers Association in Macedonia and Thrace.
Another was at the office of Thessaloniki Bar Association President Manolis Lamtsidis.
Molotov cocktails were also hurled at the home of a senior member of a local news organisation and the offices of a hotel.
(Eleftherotypia, Ta Nea - 30/11/09)
